name: iOne Resources
overview:
Teledata Communications is a premier systems integration company providing consulting, design, engineering and implementation of turnkey business communications solutions. As your trusted partner, Teledata Communications can implement comprehensive solutions including network assessments, project management, IP Telephony, LAN/WAN implementation, and 24/7 support. Ranked by Telecom Business Magazine as one of the top 500 firms in the competitive communications marketplace, Teledata Communications provides a partnership with our clients to evaluate how technology can provide your company with a competitive edge.

Teledata Communications is the oldest, most respected ShoreTel Partner in the Kansas City area. Teledata Communications is proud to be a ShoreTel Certified Orange Partner. ShoreTel Certified Orange Partners are required to maintain the highest standards for technical expertise and customer satisfaction.
